{"tid":568932,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"容祖兒喺倫敦搭地鐵時自拍並大讚等候時間短，被的士司機曲解成撐Uber怒插！","createTime":"2018-02-22T08:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T13:11:53.000Z","uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"650428932180b35deb3063a5ac26f65ec1456997","tid":568932,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"躺著也中槍！女歌手容祖兒在倫敦搭地鐵，一時興起發自拍照並讚「underground」 （地鐵）有效率，結果慘一名的士司機被曲解為支持網上電召車營辦商Uber，結果帖文在網上瘋傳。雖然帖文已經刪除，但已笑爆網民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180222/_2018022216413669617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180222%2F_2018022216413669617.jpg&h=8b581af3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1146197/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1146197%2F&d=mH%2FbgbV%2BaJJvztP6IiC7pTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=fd280d88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1146197%2F&h=73de1233\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1146197/</a>"},{"pid":"8351281ea14ad4c6068cff1189d6ed4ba89032aa","tid":568932,"uid":1886,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:57:30.000Z","msg":"容祖兒近日在英國倫敦外遊，她在Facebook帳戶上載一張在地鐵內的自拍照，並指：「taxi 45分鐘 ，underground 15分鐘 仲駛揀嘅」，讚搭地鐵比搭的士快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n不過有的士司機懷疑一時之快錯將「underground」看成「Uber」 ，並在facebook的士群組出言批評「唔好玩啦五分鐘都唔等啦，幫烏龜爸賣廣告？」。迅速引起大批網民嘲諷，「uber同underground都唔識分」。"},{"pid":"74c9d31cd553cbdb74c196ce0a735f7f240769ad","tid":568932,"uid":1886,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"有人估計發文者「可能以為人地講UNDERGROUND = 唔見得光嘅的士」。有人更改圖「抽水」將祖兒的背景改成一輛Uber私家車。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180222/_2018022216413695499.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180222%2F_2018022216413695499.jpg&h=59717752&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d1ee1e71a9a4bd8b7cfdb27f65203ab8c725307c","tid":568932,"uid":7446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"Dc9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d96aa368694b07a52000fa36e0c91f8aeec657e","tid":568932,"uid":4285,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"淨係識個&quot;U&quot; 字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5dc28c2311dd7828c2f9eeba783fd9bf3ea3f20","tid":568932,"uid":121249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"成班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded1a6106c3e3b8ef033255d5c009f1bea36f1cd","tid":568932,"uid":138355,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:06:24.000Z","msg":"隻眼殘到咁 點敢坐佢部車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b834e2a422a7e716fbc7eb03114b7a90ef346811","tid":568932,"uid":171107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"潮聯出文盲"},{"pid":"0e3cb21a8c7222f0188888fe9ddd569d984900f4","tid":568932,"uid":19613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:08:21.000Z","msg":"underground 都叫有效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50675024fb5a54a6c8c5304d7f6399b6395ab011","tid":568932,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:09:29.000Z","msg":"烏龜爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df34fa794e4476192fd94ffdcba96307d5d68812","tid":568932,"uid":169468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"的士佬柒撚到，唔識英文下次google translate左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab76cf08adb68ccae838e8cf655966c0be330a2","tid":568932,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f511f7cc7f07d44af1b0bf4d41339e0b94e7a4e","tid":568932,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25b2c7e8bb6c8400532e7666b65ffe348022202","tid":568932,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:13:55.000Z","msg":"translate server error"},{"pid":"86f6cffd62bceac952ad4de08e460b2df97da56f","tid":568932,"uid":57480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"舔共舔到傻左"},{"pid":"726b4eaeb89487cea562f00617ede9670bce2b01","tid":568932,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb9b5c2f8d77d36a9fcb78fcaf41438f5744bf6","tid":568932,"uid":74858,"like":1,"dislike